Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道你是不是很愛玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,工作的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,就喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我蠻色的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,社長幾歲啊 52
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,講出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,社長這樣講
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡怎樣的類型呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡成熟的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:18:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,證券公司社長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.01,0:18:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你的菜嗎？對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊抱歉
